OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780060267
OL,3,CAid supplies reach heart of DRC's
OL,4,CEbola outbreak as country struggles to
OL,5,Ccope
OL,7,FA white cargo plane with aid donated
OL,8,Fby the European Union flew to the
OL,9,Fnortheastern town of Bunia and UN-
OL,10,Fbranded forklifts lifted several cases
OL,11,Finto trucks.
OL,13,FHealth workers with scant supplies
OL,14,Fhave been struggling to contain an
OL,15,Foutbreak of the Bundibugyo virus, a
OL,16,Fkind of Ebola that has no approved
OL,17,Ftreatment or vaccine.
OL,19,FIn some areas, doctors have resorted
OL,20,Fto wearing expired medical masks while
OL,21,Ftreating suspected patients.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780060267
OL,3,CAid supplies reach heart of DRC's
OL,4,CEbola outbreak as country struggles to
OL,5,Ccope
OL,7,FTensions have been heightened by anger
OL,8,Famong locals over strict medical
OL,9,Fprotocols for handling victims'
OL,10,Fbodies, which conflict with
OL,11,Ftraditional burial rites.
OL,13,FAt least three attacks on health
OL,14,Fcentres have been reported in
OL,15,Fnortheastern Ituri province.
OL,17,FAid donated by the EU is expected to
OL,18,Farrive in batches over the next eight
OL,19,Fdays, Jerome Kouachi, head of
OL,20,Femergency operations at UNICEF in
OL,21,FCongo, told The Associated Press.
OL,26,@{D@Hrr{D@Jsw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
