OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780060268
OL,3,CAid supplies reach heart of DRC's
OL,4,CEbola outbreak as country struggles to
OL,5,Ccope
OL,7,FWorld Health Organization Director-
OL,8,FGeneral Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus was
OL,9,Fon his way to Congo to see the efforts
OL,10,Ffirst-hand efforts. The WHO has
OL,11,Fdeclared the outbreak a public health
OL,12,Femergency of international concern, in
OL,13,Fthe hope of ramping up aid.
OL,15,FThe Congolese government has confirmed
OL,16,Fmore than 1,000 suspected cases, with
OL,17,Fat least 220 deaths, since it declared
OL,18,Fan outbreak on May 15. But the virus
OL,19,Fhad been spreading undetected for
OL,20,Fweeks, and the WHO suspects it is much
OL,21,Flarger than what has been reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
