CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780060268
OL,3,CAid supplies reach heart of DRC's
OL,4,CEbola outbreak as country struggles to
OL,5,Ccope
OL,7,FThe virus has also reached neighboring
OL,8,FUganda, which has confirmed seven
OL,9,Fcases and one death.
OL,11,FWHO also believes the true scale of
OL,12,Fthe outbreak is much larger, as the
OL,13,Fvirus had been spreading undetected
OL,14,Ffor weeks.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday, the first survivor was
OL,17,Fdischarged from a health centre, the
OL,18,FCongolese government said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
