OL,3,CAid supplies reach heart of DRC's
OL,4,CEbola outbreak as country struggles to
OL,5,Ccope
OL,7,FIn early May, the ADF killed at least
OL,8,F40 people and burned homes in the area.
OL,10,FCases have also been reported in the
OL,11,Fneighbouring provinces of North Kivu
OL,12,Fand South Kivu, where the Rwanda-
OL,13,Fbacked M23 rebel group controls major
OL,14,Fcities including Goma and Bukavu.
OL,16,FThe main airport in Goma, a key hub
OL,17,Ffor humanitarian operations, has been
OL,18,Fclosed since January 2025, when M23
OL,19,Fseized the city.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
